OL,3,CLead engineer on Tyne Bridge
OL,4,Crestoration thanks commuters for
OL,5,Cpatience
OL,7,FThe lead engineer on the restoration
OL,8,Fof the Tyne Bridge has thanked
OL,9,Fcommuters for their patience after the
OL,10,Fbridge's traffic capacity was
OL,11,Feffectively halved.
OL,13,FOn 2 April 2024, Newcastle City
OL,14,FCouncil engineers began works to
OL,15,Fpreserve the bridge in time for its
OL,16,Fcentenary in 2028.
