OL,4,Crestoration thanks commuters for
OL,5,Cpatience
OL,7,FPamela Holmes, Assistant Director of
OL,8,FTransport at Newcastle City Council,
OL,9,Fsaid: "We want to thank commuters who
OL,10,Fhave listened to our advice over the
OL,11,Ffirst fortnight of works on the Tyne
OL,12,FBridge.
OL,14,F"This is a huge project for the
OL,15,Fregion. We are restoring a national
OL,16,Ficon and we know the entire region
OL,17,Fwants to see the bridge back to its
OL,18,Fbest.
