OL,3,CLead engineer on Tyne Bridge
OL,4,Crestoration thanks commuters for
OL,5,Cpatience
OL,7,F"We know that reducing the number of
OL,8,Flanes on the bridge does cause
OL,9,Fdisruption on routes into the city
OL,10,Fcentre, particularly at rush hour.
OL,12,F"That is why we have been so vocal in
OL,13,Frecent weeks, in the lead up to the
OL,14,Fclosures being put in place, so we can
OL,15,Fminimise that disruption as much as
OL,16,Fpossible."
