OL,3,CLead engineer on Tyne Bridge
OL,4,Crestoration thanks commuters for
OL,5,Cpatience
OL,7,FThe works will see over 900 steelwork
OL,8,Frepairs carried out as well as grit
OL,9,Fblasting and re-painting, concrete
OL,10,Frepairs, drainage improvements,
OL,11,Fstonework and masonry repairs, bridge
OL,12,Fdeck waterproofing and resurfacing,
OL,13,Fparapet protection and bridge joint
OL,14,Freplacement.
OL,16,FFor the duration of the repairs, the
OL,17,Fbridge has been reduced to one lane in
OL,18,Feach direction, effectively halving
OL,19,Fthe capacity of a route used by 70,000
OL,20,Fvehicles a day.
