OL,4,Crestoration thanks commuters for
OL,5,Cpatience
OL,7,FThe first two weeks of lane closures
OL,8,Fhas seen the expected increase in
OL,9,Fjourney times, the council said.
OL,11,FIn figures they released, they said
OL,12,Fthey have seen an average peak journey
OL,13,Ftime travelling north from Gateshead
OL,14,FStadium to the bridge of 18 minutes in
OL,15,Fthe morning, and 14 in the evening.
OL,17,FTravelling southbound from Cowgate
OL,18,Fjunction to the bridge, the average
OL,19,Fjourney time was 10 minutes in the
OL,20,Fmorning and 24 minutes in the evening,
OL,21,Fthey said.
